name: AAAHP 4th National Conference and Trade Expo
content: AAAHP is proud to be presenting its 4th National conference in 2019\. The conference is designed for Anaesthetic Technicians, Anaesthetic Nurses, and any other health care workers interested in Anaesthesia. GET IN EARLY, EARLY BIRD REGISTRATIONS END 31/07/2019.. LIMITED SPACES AVAILABLE The Venue for this years conference is the Cairns Hilton Hotel.Your gateway to the GREAT BARRIER REEF. Cairns Esplanade, lined with bars and restaurants, has a swimming lagoon. Northwest of the city, Daintree National Park spans mountainous rainforest, gorges and beaches.
